                <h1>Highway DSL v2.0.0</h1>
                <p class="tagline">Domain-Specific Language for Workflow Definition and Serialization</p>

                <div class="status-bar">
                    <span class="item"><span class="label">STATUS:</span> <span class="value">LTS-STABLE</span></span>
                    <span class="item"><span class="label">OPERATORS:</span> <span class="value">10</span></span>
